542
00:41:10,760 --> 00:41:12,420
Great.

543
00:41:12,420 --> 00:41:14,799
I am Xiao Feng. I am 31 years old.

544
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:16,279
May I know how old you are?

545
00:41:16,280 --> 00:41:18,420
I am Yelv Ji.

546
00:41:18,420 --> 00:41:20,680
I am 13 years older than you.

547
00:41:20,680 --> 00:41:22,079
Then, you are my elder brother.

548
00:41:22,080 --> 00:41:23,160
Let us...

549
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:24,879
