550
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:26,040
- All right!
- After you!

551
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:36,039
Brother!

552
00:41:36,040 --> 00:41:37,640
Elder Brother!

553
00:41:41,960 --> 00:41:44,919
Brother, are you a Khitan?

554
00:41:44,919 --> 00:41:49,100
To be honest, I am indeed a Khitan.

555
00:41:49,860 --> 00:41:53,220
Brother, it is bitter cold on Jurchen land.

556
00:41:53,220 --> 00:41:56,799
Why don't you follow me back to Shangjing and enjoy a wealthy life together?

557
00:41:56,799 --> 00:41:58,519
Thank you for your kindness.

558
00:41:58,520 --> 00:42:00,299
But I have been poor.

559
00:42:00,299 --> 00:42:02,120
When I live with the Jurchen,

560
