572
00:42:47,900 --> 00:42:51,879
With such a spirit, I believe you must be of high standing among the Khitan.

573
00:42:51,879 --> 00:42:54,019
If anything happens to you here,

574
00:42:54,019 --> 00:42:57,080
the Khitan definitely will not let it off easily.

